pan></span></div><div>It looked like soggy toilet paper. It probably hadn't been completely stripped in a couple of decades.  Just scrubbed and top coated.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xCPRwCn.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Down to bare terrazzo.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6IbKJjB.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>5 coats of finish later and finally done.  No more scratches.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/fCSJH8k</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[AvsFreak]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Dude is like...&quot;Stop disturbing me&quot;</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/3M2YGAL</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1kQcCE5.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/3M2YGAL</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[brownlumi]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Chemical art</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/NXPDdPh</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/kV8bXLg.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://youtu.be/OMBFwWTJy-0?si=6USNBMwpve6_rnd6</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/NXPDdPh</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[sjoezer]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Thursday March 27 is the last day of Earth?</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/knBqmpZ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7KTUDU9.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://imgur.com/gallery/day-hath-finally-come-QQlIhSn</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/knBqmpZ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[KatieMeme101]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Jebus</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/yyWx3dk</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/EGLADLq.png" style="max-wid